PHASE 2: THE BASS LEAD (FILTHY WOBBLE & GROWL)\
Multi-oscillator FM synthesis bass: layered sines + gritty modulators creating rubbery-metallic yet filthy, slithering timbre. Heavy modulated resonant filter (low-pass/band-pass) for organic wobble and evolving movement. Expressive downward pitch envelopes + subtle MPE-style bends on every note.  \
Processing: crushed into aggressive brick via brutal OTT-style multiband compression; light saturation/distortion for added filth and harmonics without mud.  \
Rhythm: sparse, impactful note placement \'97 each sound evolves internally through modulation rather than rapid gating. Let the wobble and filter movement carry the aggression.\

