PHASE 3: THE SPATIAL VOID\
Core signals mono-locked and dead-center.  \
Off-beat only: ultra-sparse randomized panned micro-foley (hydraulic hiss, glass shatter, guttural breath/grunt).  \
Master sidechain triggered by the kick: total annihilation of everything (including noise floor) into vast, engineered silence \'97 the voids must feel heavier than the drops.\
Deliver cold, clinical, high-impact minimalism. Textural brutality through subtraction. Maximum psychoacoustic weight via sub mass and silence. Raw, uncompromised, anti-mainstream filth.\
